{"type": "article", "id": 4093, "title": "Teca 原木玻璃混搭灯具", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-04T08:30:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052334036PAGZUVxsX9qha8b.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日前，意大利设计公司 Slow Wood 携手手工匠 Lorenzo Franceschinis 与 Shiina + Nardi 设计工作室带来一款名为「Teca」的灯具。Teca 选用了樱桃木为原材料来制作，经 Lorenzo Franceschinis 之手完成的木雕工程异常精细，在此基础上，设计团队又为其加了一层人工吹制的玻璃灯罩，创造出木雕与玻璃的对比效果，使 Teca 显出混搭的效果，灯光自木雕内罩透出再经过玻璃灯罩的过滤，显得柔和而又富有层次感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334004oSL3cXbMA8qlGJz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233401aQuIloT2d4yB1pxM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233401MZjmzH1n2A45OlPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233402xuHX67mQAIqY1Wzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233402G51sKSDdinUy9BQm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}